skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: duke bus times
des:
Ask Alexa which buses are coming to nearby stops at Duke University. Launch the skill and name a stop to find out when the buses are coming. 


Note: This skill is student made and has no formal affiliation with Duke University. Bus Times may be inaccurate. Feel free to build off of my work and adapt the skill for your campus.
Git Repo: https://github.com/IsaacAndersen/transloc-skill
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
